# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok chinese schools will be held liable for legal charges if they expel students or arrange improper courses , a senior legislator said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (l / legislator
                        :mod (s2 / senior))))
      :ARG1 (h2 / hold-02
            :ARG1 (l2 / liable-01
                  :ARG1 (s3 / school
                        :mod (c / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "China")))
                  :ARG2 (c2 / charge-05
                        :ARG1 s3
                        :ARG1-of (l3 / legal-02)))
            :condition (o / or
                  :op1 (e / expel-01
                        :ARG0 s3
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :ARG0-of (s4 / study-01)))
                  :op2 (a / arrange-01
                        :ARG0 s3
                        :ARG1 (c3 / course
                              :mod (p3 / proper
                                    :polarity -))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the presidential office confirmed today that taiwan 's united nations bid this year will sidestep the thorny question of what name the country should use to apply , and instead focus on securing taiwan 's `` participation '' in the organization .
# ::alignments
(c / confirm-01
      :ARG0 (o / office
            :mod (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG2 (p2 / president))))
      :ARG1 (s / sidestep-01
            :ARG0 (b / bid-03
                  :ARG0 (c2 / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Taiwan"))
                  :ARG1 (n2 / nation
                        :ARG1-of (u / unite-01))
                  :time (y / year
                        :mod (t / this)))
            :ARG1 (q / question-01
                  :ARG1 (t2 / thing
                        :ARG2-of (n3 / name-01)
                        :ARG1-of (u2 / use-01
                              :ARG0 c2
                              :ARG2 (a / apply-01
                                    :ARG0 c2
                                    :ARG1 t2)
                              :ARG1-of (r / recommend-01)))
                  :mod (t3 / thorny))
            :ARG1-of (ii / instead-of-91
                  :ARG2 (f / focus-01
                        :ARG0 b
                        :ARG2 (s2 / secure-01
                              :ARG0 b
                              :ARG1 (p3 / participate-01
                                    :ARG0 c2
                                    :ARG1 n2)))))
      :time (t4 / today))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok <unk> forces thursday began a high court legal challenge to the results of a referendum last november that narrowly overturned the republic 's constitutional ban on divorce .
# ::alignments
(b / begin-01
      :ARG0 (f / force
            :mod (l / law))
      :ARG1 (c / challenge-01
            :ARG0 f
            :ARG1 (r / result-01
                  :ARG1 (r2 / referendum
                        :time (d / date-entity
                              :month 11
                              :mod (l2 / last))
                        :ARG0-of (o / overturn-01
                              :ARG1 (b2 / ban-01
                                    :ARG0 (r3 / republic)
                                    :ARG1 (d2 / divorce-01)
                                    :mod (c2 / constitution))
                              :ARG1-of (n / narrow-02))))
            :location (h / high-court))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok trying to determine if the thick haze over southeast asia was a factor , investigators on saturday sifted through the wreckage of an indonesian jetliner carrying ### people that crashed in an area of sumatra clouded with smoke from hundreds of forest fires .
# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (ii / investigate-01))
      :ARG1 (w / wreckage
            :part-of (j / jetliner
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Indonesia"))
                  :ARG0-of (c2 / carry-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :mod (c3 / country-region
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "South"
                                          :op2 "Asia"))
                              :ARG0-of (c4 / crash-01
                                    :location (a / area
                                          :mod (m / mountain
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Sumatra"))
                                          :ARG1-of (c5 / cloud-01
                                                :ARG0 (s2 / smoke
                                                      :source (f / fire
                                                            :mod (f2 / forest)
                                                            :quant (m2 / multiple
                                                                  :op1 100))))))))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s3 / saturday))
      :purpose (t / try-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (d2 / determine-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (t2 / truth-value
                        :polarity-of (f3 / factor-01
                              :ARG0 (h / haze
                                    :ARG1-of (t3 / thick-03)
                                    :location (s4 / southeast))
                              :ARG1 j)))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :ARG1 (s2 / share
                  :ARG1-of (n / new-01))

                  :value ".##"
                  :ARG1-of (f / follow-01
                        :ARG2 (d2 / dive-01
                              :ARG1 (m / market
                                    :poss (w / we)))))
            :time (d3 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / tuesday))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (m / move-01

                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Pakistan"))
                  :ARG2 (a / ahead
                        :prep-with (e / elect-01
                              :ARG1-of (f / free-04)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s / sunday))
      :concession-of (d2 / decline-02
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (f2 / force-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 c3
                  :ARG2 (h / hold-04
                        :ARG0 c3
                        :ARG1 (d3 / day
                              :time-of (e2 / elect-01)
                              :ARG1-of (s2 / schedule-01))))))

# ::alignments
(m / multi-sentence
      :snt1 (o / open-02
            :ARG1 (t / thing
                  :ARG2-of (p / price-01
                        :ARG1 (s / share))
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Japan")))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / tuesday))
            :ARG1-of (l / low-04
                  :ARG2-of (h / have-degree-91
                        :ARG1 t
                        :ARG3 (m2 / more)))
            :time (e / exchange-01
                  :ARG1 (s2 / stock)
                  :mod (c2 / company
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Tkyo"))))
      :snt2 (f / fall-01
            :ARG1 (a / average-01
                  :ARG1 (s3 / stock
                        :mod (c3 / company
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Nikkei"))))
            :ARG4 (p2 / point
                  :mod (o2 / or
                        :op1 (p3 / percent)
                        :op2 (p4 / percentage-entity)))
            :time (a2 / after
                  :op1 (t3 / trade-01
                        :quant (t4 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 5
                              :unit (m3 / minute)
                              :ord (o3 / ordinal-entity
                                    :value 1))))))

      :ARG0 (p / person

                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "U.S."))
                  :ARG2 (o / official)))
      :ARG1 (ii / injure-01
            :ARG0 (h2 / hit-01
                  :ARG0 (v / vehicle
                        :poss (p2 / person
                              :quant 2
                              :ARG0-of h
                              :ARG1 (o2 / operation
                                    :ARG1-of (s2 / special-02))
                              :ARG2 (s3 / soldier))))
            :ARG1 (d / device
                  :ARG1-of (e / explode-01
                        :ARG1-of (p3 / possible-01)))
            :location (e2 / east
                  :part-of (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Afghanistan"))))
      :ARG1 p2
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday)))
